## What's cut from v1 (mid-July 2026 launch)

From the 11 pillars, what's fully shipped at launch:
- Pillars 1-5 (polished)
- Pillar 6 (Running the Home) in v1 form
- Pillars 7-11 scaffolded but marked "coming soon"

From feature ambitions, what's NOT in v1:
- Native iOS app
- Native Android app
- Plaid banking integration (CSV import only)
- Voice-based anything (voice meal logging, voice Cy)
- Photo-based meal logging
- Auto-meal-planning from recipes
- Real-time collaborative editing
- Video content library (podcast embeds only)
- Marketplace / content from external creators
- Community / forum features
- Church Pack admin UI
- Multi-household support (one household per subscription)
- Multi-language (English only for v1)
- Offline mode
- Advanced reporting / analytics for families

