- 5 paying families actively using daily
- All five have completed at least 4 Family Meetings
- Cy voice feels right to all five
- No critical bugs
- NPS from the five: 40+

### End of 2026
- 50-100 paying families
- Monthly churn under 5%
- Cy interaction quality consistent across all households
- Content library has 30+ items integrated into pillars
- Running the Home pillar is stable and loved
- Families are generating their own content inside pillars
  (notes, check-ins, rituals)

### End of 2027
- 500 paying families
- All 11 pillars in at least beta
- Pillar 11 (When It's Hard) carefully shipped
- Native mobile apps
- Church Pack pilot with 3-5 churches

