## The product's north star

**A family opens Trellis on a Tuesday morning. The house feels
lighter.**

That's the test. Every feature, every release, every Cy
interaction should make Tuesday morning lighter. If a feature
makes Tuesday harder, we don't ship it.

Everything else is detail.
